article.description: — Melvin Council Jr.'s 18 points helped Wagner defeat NJIT 64-51 on Saturday.
article.headline: Council scores 18 and Wagner wins 64-51 against NJIT
article.linkText: Council scores 18 and Wagner wins 64-51 against NJIT
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Melvin Council Jr.'s 18 points helped Wagner defeat NJIT 64-51 on Saturday. Council had five rebounds for the Seahawks (2-3). Javier Esquerra Trelles scored 12 points and added four steals. Tariq Francis finished with 17 points and two steals for the Highlanders (1-4). Sebastian Robinson added 11 points for NJIT. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
